content.html: I have NEVER heard an older woman say: “I wish I would’ve sacrificed my youth for a man.” “I wish I would’ve dressed more conservatively.” “I wish I wouldn’t have gotten an education and built a career before starting a family.” But you know what I do hear them say?? 🥴
content.value:
I have NEVER heard an older woman say:

 “I wish I would’ve sacrificed my youth for a man.”

“I wish I would’ve dressed more conservatively.” 

“I wish I wouldn’t have gotten an education and built a career before starting a family.” 

But you know what I do hear them say?? 🥴
